---
description: Enforce relative imports within packages; never import from src/ roots
alwaysApply: true
---

# Relative Imports Only

- Within a package, always use relative import paths (`./`, `../`).
- Never generate imports that start with `src/` or `test/`.
- Across packages, import from the package name (`@base/core`, `@base/design-system`), never deep paths.
